Description: Selection of the data set number after the end of asequence.0 / DataSetSelect: Data set is set via the signalinput function "Data Set Select"1 / Automatic: Data set is set automaticallyValue 0: After the end of a sequence, the selecteddata set must be set via the signal input function"Data Set Select".Value 1: After the end of a sequence, the selecteddata set is set automatically.Setting can only be modified if power stage isdisabled.Modified settings become active immediately.Available with firmware version â‰¥V01.09.
